I"”<h1 id="account">Account</h1>

<h3 id="step-1-install-polkadot-chrome-extension">Step 1: Install Polkadot Chrome Extension</h3>

<p><strong>Use Chrome</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Go to: <a href="https://polkadot.js.org/extension/ ">https://polkadot.js.org/extension/ <a></a></a></li>
  <li>Click Download for Chrome</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step1.png" /></p>

<h3 id="step-2-create-an-account">Step 2: Create an account</h3>

<p><strong>Using your Polkadot chrome wallet extension</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Click the plus sign in the top left</li>
  <li>Choose Create new account</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step2a.png" /></p>
